# Security Headers
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' https://plausible.io https://static.cloudflareinsights.com https://identity.netlify.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: https:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://plausible.io https://cloudflareinsights.com https://identity.netlify.com; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self';
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload

